			<div id="c385" class="infobox ce-text"><article role="article"><div class="csc-header csc-header-n1"><h4 class="divider csc-firstHeader">Kontakt</h4></div><section class="content-padding"><p class="bodytext"><b>Bundesgeschäftsstelle DIE LINKE</b><br /> Kleine Alexanderstraße 28<br />10178 Berlin<br />Telefon: (030) 24 009 0<br />Telefax: (030) 24 110 46<br />c/o: Tanju Tügel<br /><a href="mailto:tanju.tuegel@die-linke.de" class="mail">tanju.tuegel@die-linke.de</a></p></section></article></div>
